// 12-paper-demos/resource_raii.yx
// 验证: 资源管理 RAII 模式
// 论文价值: 令牌天然保证资源生命周期

use std.io

File: Type = {
    name: String,
    closed: Bool
}

File.open: (self: &mut File) -> Void = {
    self.closed = false
    io.println("opening file")
}

File.close: (self: &mut File) -> Void = {
    self.closed = true
    io.println("closing file")
}

main = {
    f = File("test.txt", true)
    f.open()
    f.close()
    io.println("ALL TESTS PASSED")
}
